'''Slightly Mad Studios''' 是一間[[英國|英國]]的獨立電子遊戲公司，總部設於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[倫敦|倫敦]]。2009年1月12日，它收購了 Blimey! Games 軟體研發公司<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mobygames.com/company/blimey-games-ltd |title=MobyGames: Blimey! Games |publisher=[[MobyGames|MobyGames]] |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2009-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221021906/http://www.mobygames.com/company/blimey-games-ltd |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.develop-online.net/news/31082/Blimey-goes-Slightly-Mad |title=Blimey! goes Slightly Mad | Game Development | News by Develop |publisher=Develop-online.net |date=2009-01-12 |accessdate=2010-11-30 |archive-date=2009-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091006084815/http://www.develop-online.net/news/31082/Blimey-goes-Slightly-Mad |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2009年9月，它經由[[美国艺电|美国艺电]]發行《[[極速快感：進化世代|極速快感：進化世代]]》<ref>{{cite web |last=Crossley |first=Rob |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/news/ea-dates-need-speed-shift-release |title=EA Dates Need For Speed Shift Release | Edge Magazine |publisher=Next-gen.biz |date=2009-03-23 |accessdate=2010-11-30 |archive-date=2012-09-11 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120911234355/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/ea-dates-need-speed-shift-release |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2019年11月，英国老牌游戏公司[[Codemaster|Codemaster]]宣布以3000万美元收购Slightly Mad Studios。<ref>[https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-11-28-codemasters-acquires-project-cars-dev-slightly-mad-studios Codemasters acquires Project CARS dev Slightly Mad Studios] {{Wayback|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2019-11-28-codemasters-acquires-project-cars-dev-slightly-mad-studios |date=20191129045112 }}.Eurogamer.2019-11-28.[2019-11-29].</ref>

2010年，在百大研發名單之中，它名列第17位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://issuu.com/develop/docs/develop100_2010 |title=Develop 100 - 2010 Edition |publisher=Issuu.com |date=2010-05-05 |accessdate=2010-11-30 |archive-date=2010-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101115155841/http://issuu.com/develop/docs/develop100_2010 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

